According to JPMorgan analyst Samik Chatterjee, Apple plans to release four new iPhone models in 2020. All new iPhone models will feature OLED displays and 5G connectivity.

iPhone 5.4-inch and 6.1-inch models
• OLDE display
• 5G (sub-6Ghz)
• Dual-lens camera

iPhone Pro 6.1-inch and 6.7-inch models
• OLED display
• 5G (mmWave)
• Triple-lens cameras
• World facing 3D sensing ———————————————————
